</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">Related</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Other commercial grill service.</h2>
    <ul class="bullet-list">
      <li><a href="/commercial/grill-repair/">Commercial grill repair (parent pillar)</a></li>
      <li><a href="/commercial/grill-repair/flame-out/">Flame out (lights then dies)</a></li>
      <li><a href="/commercial/grill-repair/grease-fire-prevention/">Grease fire prevention + Fire Marshal compliance</a></li>
