    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bottom-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Commercial grill down during service? Same-day priority.</h2>
    <p>Wolf Outdoor commercial, Lynx Pro Sear, Twin Eagles commercial, MagiKitch'n outdoor across LA, OC, Ventura. $120 commercial diagnostic, waived with repair. BHGS #A49573, EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
